{"tid":183081,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[傷殘座] 世衛定義毒撚為傷殘人士","createTime":"2017-04-01T18:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T06:25:18.000Z","uid":18844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f5fb908743de64ad3b124a16d1a7bab4b0a33b5","tid":183081,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T18:38:15.000Z","msg":"Failure to find a sexual partner is now a DISABILITY says World Health Organisation<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-images-express-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/1/590x/Sexual-partners-disability-723323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-images-express-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F1%2F590x%2FSexual-partners-disability-723323.jpg&h=72005f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPEOPLE who don&rsquo;t have sex or struggle to find a sexual partner to have children with will now be considered as DISABLED, according to barmy new guidelines set to be announced.<br />\n<br />\nBy&nbsp;REBECCA PERRING<br />\n<br />\nPUBLISHED: 08:26, Mon, Oct 24, 2016UPDATED:&nbsp;11:29, Mon, Oct 24, 2016<br />\n<br />\nShare on FacebookShare on TwitterShare on Google+Share with EmailShare via Whatsapp<br />\n<br />\nUntil now, infertility - the failure to achieve pregnancy after 12 months or more of regular unprotected sex - was not considered a disability.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nBut now in dramatic move the World Health Organisation will change the standard to suggest that a person who is unable to find a suitable sexual partner or is lacking a sexual relationship to have children - will now be equally classified as disabled.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nWHO says the change will give every individual &ldquo;the right to reproduce&rdquo;."},{"pid":"6b65a8b28a7ab5b87426ddd0716e8c3a90077f7b","tid":183081,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T18:40:15.000Z","msg":"source :<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.express.co.uk/news/uk/723323/Sexual-partner-fertility-disability-World-Health-Organisation-IVF/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2F723323%2FSexual-partner-fertility-disability-World-Health-Organisation-IVF%2Famp&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bcf1dbe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.express.co.uk/news/uk/723323/Sexual-partner-fertility-disability-World-Health-Organisation-IVF/amp</a>"},{"pid":"ea1f1475251b82e2ade19edcaf8564da55bdb237","tid":183081,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T19:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89fc512ae12411aaf86cef0863d52fc04c0fbc1","tid":183081,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T19:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c0f3f8fb204d092cf6fb7f7cf575fba1fee8fa","tid":183081,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T19:22:41.000Z","msg":"搭地鐵可唔可以申請$2<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e534a45245b2741c24e474538145299a7d2a89b","tid":183081,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭地鐵可唔可以申請$2<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚慳慳埋埋咁多錢唔貪果雞碎咁多<br />\n而且係可以唔搭就唔搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402a4f4f14f7e1222a417918b9268393409e2295","tid":183081,"uid":32454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9c6f14381cfd2d8382a28f87a99d2b7e7ce597","tid":183081,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"